  <entry>
    <title>APCS 202603 題解</title>
    <url>/0cy/APCS-202603-%E9%A1%8C%E8%A7%A3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="p1-比例分割"><a href="#p1-比例分割" class="headerlink" title="p1 比例分割"></a>p1 比例分割</h2><p><a href="https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s179">https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s179</a></p>
<h3 id="考點"><a href="#考點" class="headerlink" title="考點"></a>考點</h3><p>二分搜、前綴和</p>
<h3 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h3><p>看到題目頻繁的求區間和且沒有動態修改，可以利用前綴和在 $O(1)$ 內求出區間和。<br>然後 k 可以利用對區間和二分搜，直到找出要的答案 (考試時我沒想到要對區間和做二分搜，只想到對 L~R，但沒單調性只好作罷)，這樣總複雜度是 $O(n + m \log n)$。</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> int long long</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> p[<span class="number">100005</span>];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">signed</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	ios::<span class="built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	cin.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="type">int</span> n, m;</span><br><span class="line">	cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	p[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">		cin &gt;&gt; x;</span><br><span class="line">		p[i] = p[i - <span class="number">1</span>] + x;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">while</span> (m--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> l, r, a, b;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; l &gt;&gt; r &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> le = l, ri = r, ans = <span class="number">0</span>; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> st = p[r] - p[l - <span class="number">1</span>];   </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> target = a * st;        </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (le &lt;= ri) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> k = (le + ri) / <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> s2 = p[k] - p[l - <span class="number">1</span>]; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (s2 * (a + b) &gt;= target) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                ans = k;       </span><br><span class="line">                ri = k - <span class="number">1</span>;    </span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                le = k + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="p2-觀光旅遊"><a href="#p2-觀光旅遊" class="headerlink" title="p2 觀光旅遊"></a>p2 觀光旅遊</h2><p><a href="https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s180">https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s180</a></p>
<h3 id="考點-1"><a href="#考點-1" class="headerlink" title="考點"></a>考點</h3><p>排序、二分搜</p>
<h3 id="思路-1"><a href="#思路-1" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h3><p>先對 t 排序，方便做二分搜。<br>輸入的 s 跟 e 其實就是左右邊界，<code>it_start</code> 是 t 中第一個大於等於 s 的 iterator ; <code>it_end</code> 是 t 中第一個不在範圍的 iterator，兩者相減就是範圍內的數量。複雜度是 $O((n+m) \log n)$。</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> int long long</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">signed</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ios_base::<span class="built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cin.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> n, m;</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">t</span><span class="params">(n)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; t[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">sort</span>(t.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(), t.<span class="built_in">end</span>());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> total_watches = <span class="number">0</span>; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; m; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> s, e;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; s &gt;&gt; e;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">auto</span> it_start = <span class="built_in">lower_bound</span>(t.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(), t.<span class="built_in">end</span>(), s);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">auto</span> it_end = <span class="built_in">upper_bound</span>(t.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(), t.<span class="built_in">end</span>(), e);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        total_watches += (it_end - it_start);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; total_watches &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="p3-校運代表隊"><a href="#p3-校運代表隊" class="headerlink" title="p3 校運代表隊"></a>p3 校運代表隊</h2><p><a href="https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s181">https://zerojudge.tw/ShowProblem?problemid=s181</a></p>
<h3 id="考點-2"><a href="#考點-2" class="headerlink" title="考點"></a>考點</h3><p>dfs 遞迴窮舉</p>
<h3 id="思路-2"><a href="#思路-2" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h3><p>對每個條件都開個陣列紀錄，dfs(u) 代表現在正在決定「要不要選第 u 號學生」。</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> int long long</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n, m, r, k, t;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> good_at[<span class="number">105</span>];    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> class_cnt[<span class="number">25</span>];   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> type_used[<span class="number">15</span>];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> current_cnt = <span class="number">0</span>; </span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; res;    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 第 u 號學生</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">dfs</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (res.<span class="built_in">size</span>() == k) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        current_cnt++; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (current_cnt == t) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                cout &lt;&lt; res[i] &lt;&lt; (i == k - <span class="number">1</span> ? <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">0</span>); </span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (u &gt; m * r) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> class_id = (u - <span class="number">1</span>) / r + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> skill = good_at[u];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!type_used[skill] &amp;&amp; class_cnt[class_id] &lt; <span class="number">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        res.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(u);</span><br><span class="line">        type_used[skill] = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        class_cnt[class_id]++;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">dfs</span>(u + <span class="number">1</span>); </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        res.<span class="built_in">pop_back</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        type_used[skill] = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        class_cnt[class_id]--;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 不選</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">dfs</span>(u + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">signed</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ios_base::<span class="built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cin.<span class="built_in">tie</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!(cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m &gt;&gt; r &gt;&gt; k &gt;&gt; t)) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> total_students = m * r;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= total_students; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; good_at[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">dfs</span>(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
